name: Got no money? (FREE)
description:
So why would you want this print?
well... Lets face it, it isn't one of my best, but its (almost)** free, so i guess if;
you're a student,
you've got no job,
you don't support artists...
... (if you did you would be buying a lovely quality piece on card.)
or you just want one. (fair enough, its free**.)

They're economy prints on economy A4 paper, but they dont cost you squat** so quit complaining. 

*Maximum three per household. 
*flat rate worldwide postage Â£0.99 - come on thats fair.

** Bigcartel who runs my store wont let me set the price to 0, so it has to be 0.01, sorry!

This image is in the public domain, feel free to use for commercial or personal use. just because i'm a nice guy.

name: JUST SAY NO
description:
This is my most recent piece.
the prints are a4 and are printed 
on high quality card and is full colour.

would be great as a greeting card 
decorative hanging, well pretty much anything 
an a4 picture is good for.

I am able to print these on t-shirts, email me if you're interested: Joe@alxbyd.co.uk
